Support internal audit, enterprise risk management, financial due diligence, and other advisory work.

Trainee to be involved in:
1. Perform test of internal controls effectiveness such as vouching of transactions to underlying supporting documents, eg supplier invoices, purchase orders and delivery orders
2. Perform analytical review such as reasonableness test, trend analysis.
3. Perform data analytics to identify unusual trends or anormalies
4. Draft audit findings
5. Communicate effectively within the team and with clients

Technical Skills and Competencies Trainee will learn
1. Understand risks and controls
2. Auditing techniques
3. Report writing
4. Teamwork
5. Time management